value: ****TESTS FREE-RIDING USING THE SHARE OF A SUBJECT-GRADE THAT A TEACHER TEACHES AS THE MEASURE OF HOW MUCH OF AN AWARD THEY'RE RESPONSIBLE FOR***
***USES ALTERNATIVE MATCHING OF TEACHERS TO STUDENTS WHERE FOR STANFORD TESTS - THE TEST IN YEAR t APPLIES TO TEACHERS IN SPRING OF t - 1 and FALL OF t
***ADJUST TEACHER-STUDENT LINKS SO THAT THE STUDENT IS LINKED TO THE TEACHER FROM THE SPRING AND FALL SEMESTERS PRIOR TO STANFORD ADMINISTRATION IN JANUARY

***NOTE THAT 9TH GRADE SCIENCE AND SOC ARE STANFORD RATHER THAN TAKS IN ASPIRE****

***SCIENCE & SOC FOR 10 & 11.FOR ACROSS DEPARTMENT ANALYSIS, LIMIT TO GRADES 10 & 11****
